OL,9,CG2013FMishal Husain presents the final
OL,10,FBBC One news programme to be broadcast
OL,11,Ffrom BBC Television Centre. Mishal
OL,12,Fsigned off from studio N6 at 10.15pm,
OL,13,Fconcluding almost 45 years of broadcast
OL,14,Fnews from the building.
